    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>brown onions</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and dice the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
