      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pot with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onions</strong>, <strong>diced carrot </strong>and<strong> chopped garlic</strong>, 75ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[125ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Cook for 10 min or until the onions are very soft, stirring frequently</p>",
